section.steps-section
  .wrapper
    .steps-section__container
      img.steps-section__rose(src="images/steps-section-rose.png" loading="lazy" width="643" height="632" alt="rose")
      .steps-section__line
      h2.steps-section__title.font-s-74.font-w-zt-medium.text-up Поможем вам открыть <br> ресторан за 10 простых шагов
